From: Isuru Fernando <isuruf@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 19 Nov 2025 14:59:11 -0800
Subject: [PATCH 4/4] fix malloc error

isuruf: I have no clue why the malloc error happened in the first place
---
 gcc/common/config/aarch64/aarch64-common.cc | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/gcc/common/config/aarch64/aarch64-common.cc b/gcc/common/config/aarch64/aarch64-common.cc
index ae467f140e3..d15fcd1f852 100644
--- a/gcc/common/config/aarch64/aarch64-common.cc
+++ b/gcc/common/config/aarch64/aarch64-common.cc
@@ -749,7 +749,7 @@ aarch64_get_arch_string_for_assembler (aarch64_arch arch,
     if (entry->arch == arch)
 	break;
 
-  std::string outstr = entry->name
+  std::string outstr = std::string(entry->name)
 	+ aarch64_get_extension_string_for_isa_flags (flags, entry->flags);
 
   return outstr;
